    "name": "Weeks Till Winter",
    "steam_appid": 3262560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the table before you sits a set of books containing magic worlds and cryptic secrets. Open a book, explore its pages, and enter into varied landscapes of procedurally generated terrain and resources. Pay careful attention to the hints that litter the pages. Unlocking their meaning is the key to mastering the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/9d43b87de5686fe31ea979f1cd45be8c.avif?t=1762556424\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each world is a randomized puzzle. Learn optimized building arrangements, target resource-rich terrain tiles, and unlock larger, more rewarding structures to gain higher scores. Turn-by-turn and season-by-season, you must strategically place buildings to maximize resource and population gains while avoiding the wandering terrors of winter. Resource management is minimalistic, but skilled play requires planning and deep game knowledge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/f13bd78b94c2a59ae23f7c0dc1ae8efe.webp?t=1762556424\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/f13bd78b94c2a59ae23f7c0dc1ae8efe.poster.webp?t=1762556424\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=347 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In Summary:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place buildings on resources to harvest them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep buildings near related buildings to earn bonuses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secret building arrangements to trigger bonus structures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Undo and retry placements within a season to optimize</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your buildings during winter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/47b2e8a4da064fcd93f16b05281acf55.webp?t=1762556424\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/47b2e8a4da064fcd93f16b05281acf55.poster.webp?t=1762556424\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=347 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your population grows, you may expand to new  areas. But take care. The ruins of a failed civilization lie scattered throughout the land. They will sense your presence. And when winter comes, altars will stir, unleashing terrors held back only by heat and flame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/04ab071652432fa04f910aa4a07c0a9f.poster.avif?t=1762556424\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/04ab071652432fa04f910aa4a07c0a9f.webm?t=1762556424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/04ab071652432fa04f910aa4a07c0a9f.mp4?t=1762556424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special items can be found or purchased from a mysterious hermit. Use them to boost your population, increase resource gains, or destroy altars and winter terrors. Using these tools wisely is necessary to reach the highest rankings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/6ad70d1911ad6169313a2d3a9e3ed0df.poster.avif?t=1762556424\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/6ad70d1911ad6169313a2d3a9e3ed0df.webm?t=1762556424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/6ad70d1911ad6169313a2d3a9e3ed0df.mp4?t=1762556424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Also Included:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 puzzle-like challenge maps exploring the underlying rules of the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The level editor used to create those challenge maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A free-build mode, without time or resource constraints, to make something interesting and beautiful</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/364f8df45a5f68952e72da3ac40315a3.poster.avif?t=1762556424\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/364f8df45a5f68952e72da3ac40315a3.webm?t=1762556424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/364f8df45a5f68952e72da3ac40315a3.mp4?t=1762556424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, you may discover fragmentary manuscripts buried in the ruins of the civilization that preceded you, or otherwise hidden throughout the game world. Through voice-acted journal entries, cryptic fables, and historical records, you can piece together the forgotten lore that explains this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/8906b5f126fdd50496795c9dd81af096.avif?t=1762556424\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weeks Till Winter offers:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 different worlds of procedurally generated terrain for standard play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 puzzle-like challenge maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A free-build mode without the constraints of resource costs nor winter terrors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A level editor to build your own playable worlds or custom scenarios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lore-based fragmented narrative, with more than a dozen hidden manuscripts to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and windmills!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/5870ae4882d5b49d2ecf679b22cc4df2.webp?t=1762556424\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262560/extras/5870ae4882d5b49d2ecf679b22cc4df2.poster.webp?t=1762556424\" class=\"bb_img\" width=432 height=347 /></picture></span></p>",
